{
  "stem": "7506.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because of the physical distance involved, I don't think it, under normal circumstances, would have taken more than one overnight.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Certainly, the whole day-- that's quite possible-- and one night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I don't think more than two nights, I doubt very much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I doubt very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall being given any food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think my mother had food with us, bread and cheese, that she had with us from the camp still from Westerbork in one of those shoulder bags that we had.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The day of the final stop of the train, if I could say that, the day of arrival, I remember that was very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody knew where it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As it was in an area completely surrounded by pine trees.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were ordered out of the train onto a platform, but not a platform that's made like in a regular station, a platform more that in English is called a siding.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A siding being really a place where a train gets put to be worked on or to be left or something like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the platform, as such, wasn't made out of proper materials.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was like more earth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember getting out of the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all-- there was a platform where the train was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And behind the train-- or shall I say on the other side of the train-- were German soldiers with leather coats, rifles slung over their shoulder on their back, and virtually each one had what you call a German shepherd dog.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were on the other side of the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on this side of the train, on the platform side, were a few obvious officers with black leather coats, SS, all SS.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
